<collectingCountry box="[544,595,995,1019]" name="Indonesia" pageId="35" pageNumber="314">Flores</collectingCountry>
juveniles tantum cogniti, rubri, pedicello 
<quantity box="[447,523,1022,1046]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.5" metricValueMax="2.0" metricValueMin="1.0" pageId="35" pageNumber="314" unit="mm" value="1.5" valueMax="2.0" valueMin="1.0">1-2 mm</quantity>
longo. Sepala fere omnino libera, pro ratione elongata, 
<quantity box="[476,587,1048,1072]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.35" metricValueMax="1.5" metricValueMin="1.2" pageId="35" pageNumber="314" unit="mm" value="1.35" valueMax="1.5" valueMin="1.2">1,2-1,5 mm</quantity>
longa, margine pallida, laete undulata, sine ornamento glanduloso bene visbili vel aliquot punctis praedita.
</emphasis>
</paragraph>
